title: Ally Nakamura | About, contact, and portfolio
snippet: Hi, I'm Ally Nakamura :) I'm a Stanford new grad in SF, originally from the DMV and Tokyo. I love everything healthcare and am currently working on helping medical device companies deploy AI to make their workflows easier. On weekends you can find me hiking, going to new DJ sets, eating sushi, or playing poker with friends.
